":"734a4f72d7b2ac745766e62668796b86b2291afa","tid":833551,"uid":156543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b83d7edefeee1ff2f4610a1a9129c4631805f5","tid":833551,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1c6d2c517a809c23265fdced44d9508bf31a2475","tid":833551,"uid":156543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:03:09.000Z","msg":"認真 軍人用嘅<br />\n學林鄭話齋 正常都搭飛機啦 話知你公幹定旅行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁幾時用呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果香港再有示威 佔中咁嘅事發生 <br />\n大陸頂唔順 要派兵落黎<br />\n又要快 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/225649_d24a5444868e35021649a693e5345fc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F225649_d24a5444868e35021649a693e5345fc0.png&h=0127f0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁又未至於 入侵人國家就話要快姐 唔洗錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用兵車運 又慢得濟 落到黎骨都散啦 無曬戰鬥力點得嫁<br />\n咁高鐵 咪fit囉 <br />\n大陸不嬲都玩開嫁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/230009_7bd1ca21853ce02b25591f8cce56a528.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F230009_7bd1ca21853ce02b25591f8cce56a528.png&h=2919c534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過 聽日仲要翻工 黎多次佔中？ 唔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"ching 我由頭到尾都冇話過香港冇喎<br />\n我見多人討論話貴 我分享下姐 既然你咁都攞到優越感 我都鄧你開心嘅 <br />\n<br />\n至於上面幾位討論運坦克嘅都唔洗咁激動 <br />\n條路就鋪好咗啦 佢fit翻size 特登整多架火車 運火箭零件都得添 分享下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/s