 />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/225649_d24a5444868e35021649a693e5345fc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F225649_d24a5444868e35021649a693e5345fc0.png&h=0127f0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁又未至於 入侵人國家就話要快姐 唔洗錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用兵車運 又慢得濟 落到黎骨都散啦 無曬戰鬥力點得嫁<br />\n咁高鐵 咪fit囉 <br />\n大陸不嬲都玩開嫁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/230009_7bd1ca21853ce02b25591f8cce56a528.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F230009_7bd1ca21853ce02b25591f8cce56a528.png&h=2919c534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過 聽日仲要翻工 黎多次佔中？ 唔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"你唔係覺得班駐港部隊夠料全面控制香港吓？<br />\n打個風又炒船喺澳門救災又暈又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班港豬打完風返工完全冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你話洗唔洗運多d兵落嚟？"},{"pid":"6ca5761745abf366434a331733dba30c3d544469","tid":833551,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:07:14.000Z","msg":"有咩事上黎斷路會唔會好難認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ce32a3c911f9d73d865865a70cfff9d6c531fb","tid":833551,"uid":170772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23a0adfee390b4ae60ac5cbf91be74297afc24fc","tid":833551,"uid":203983,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"0f9bc8b4eec6f56d1506851004a53f4c2054163b","tid":833551,"uid":199334,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d2b2d6d983440fb1ad596ecf0f35905d0b0543b3","tid":833551,"uid":203983,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/202603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F202603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8c69147d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實樓主講得唔夠準確 <br />\n最主要目的係軍事用途 並非鎮壓示威<br />\n香港人示威 就算去到暴動 香港警察＋駐港解放軍絕對有能力應付<br />\n可以參考韓農示威 唔好睇少香港警察既裝備<br />\n<br />\n返正題 共產黨好明白如果發動戰爭 香港係必爭之地<br />\n所以佢地要確保海陸空所有渠道都可以作為運輸<br />\n高鐵一快二直達市中心 無論應對示威／戰爭都好<br />\n況且多一個渠道多一個保障 淨係靠深圳河 太高風險"}]}